snippet.title: He Watches Me [VN Teaser Trailer]
snippet.description:
https://morphidragunny.itch.io/he-watches-me 
The game will be available September 30th, 2022!

Sara only wants a simple life at school but when her classmate Tyler keeps watching her from the back of the room she just can't ignore it. She's tried, but something just, isn’t right...

A short psychological horror visual novel with an unfortunate ending...
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Art and Video by;
Morphi (Hot-Gothics) - https://hot-gothics.carrd.co/

Music by:
Henri Tikkala (HenkkaStorm) - https://instagram.com/henkkastorm
Sebastian Lee - https://linktr.ee/sebilee
